{
  "stem": "1736.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 390.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You've got to have certificates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We have other people waiting that want to come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can't come in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You have to go back, this, that, and the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't recall any of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I just was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had a-- No.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had a daughter with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know anything about her--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--her private life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although, I knew her very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spoke to her when I-- on a number of occasions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Recha Freier, in fact, it is claimed, and I believe it so, was the founder of Youth Aliyah, which is the international movement.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she later on went on to rescue thousands and thousands of children, picking them up off the street and bringing children in from Tehran, from all over the place, and in fact has got-- was given the Israel Prize later on and did lots and lots of good deeds.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After have crossed-- after having crossed so many borders, and difficult borders, to get into Palestine wasn't really a problem.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, in Rosh Hanikra, the-- or Rosh an-Nawakir as they called it, there were a few soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I mean, we just went back and, you know--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a normal way of going through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we just went back and fanned out across the border and just crossed in, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then gathered on the other side, and were told-- and asked, actually, did we have relatives that we wanted to go to?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did we want to go to the city, or what our wishes were?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In my own case, I didn't want to go to relatives, even though I had some.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a couple of uncles there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I want to go to kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
